103
00:11:31,769 --> 00:11:33,608
I guess not.

104
00:12:18,024 --> 00:12:20,363
Good afternoon.
Welcome to Rekall.

105
00:12:20,484 --> 00:12:22,731
Douglas Quaid.
I have an appointment.

106
00:12:26,032 --> 00:12:27,411
- Bob?
- Yeah?

107
00:12:27,575 --> 00:12:30,919
- Doug Quaid is here to see you. Okay.
- Yeah. I'll be right out.

108
00:12:31,704 --> 00:12:33,717
That'll be just one minute, Mr. Quaid.

109
00:12:34,665 --> 00:12:36,045
Thank you.

110
00:12:43,717 --> 00:12:47,603
- Doug...Paul McClane. It's good to see you.
- Nice to meet you.

111
00:12:47,605 --> 00:12:48,933
Come on in. It's through here.

112
00:12:50,639 --> 00:12:53,050
- Go and have a seat. Make yourself comfortable.
- Thank you.

113
00:12:53,934 --> 00:12:55,824
Now help me out here, Doug.

114
00:12:55,828 --> 00:12:58,581
- You were interested in a memory of--
