176
00:16:19,323 --> 00:16:22,284
Well don't worry.
Things hardly ever fuck up around here.

177
00:16:23,494 --> 00:16:25,416
Good evening... Doug.

178
00:16:25,579 --> 00:16:27,877
- I'm Dr. Lull.
