227
00:19:33,851 --> 00:19:37,688
- Let me go! Untie me now!
- Ernie, grab his leg!

228
00:19:37,772 --> 00:19:40,194
- Hold him down!
- Let me go home!

229
00:20:04,006 --> 00:20:06,178
