01:35:11,747 --> 01:35:13,419
What is it?

972
01:35:14,458 --> 01:35:15,462
There's an opening.

973
01:35:16,668 --> 01:35:18,257
I knew it.

974
01:35:46,674 --> 01:35:49,949
This whole thing is one big reactor made out of turbinium.

975
01:35:49,952 --> 01:35:53,412
Cohaagen knows it makes air.
The bastard won't turn it on.

976
01:35:53,414 --> 01:35:57,327
Of course not.
If Mars had an atmosphere, he'd lose control.

977
01:35:58,878 --> 01:36:00,216
See down there.

978
01:36:01,422 --> 01:36:03,803
It's a glacier.

979
01:36:03,924 --> 01:36:06,973
The whole core of Mars is ice.

980
01:36:07,094 --> 01:36:11,513
The reactor melts it and it releases the oxygen.

981
01:36:11,515 --> 01:36:12,812
Come on.

982
01:36:12,933 --> 01:36:16,016
- Enough for everyone to breathe?
- Sure.

983
01:36:16,020 --> 01:36:18,859
Enough for the whole planet.

984
01:36:19,023 --> 01:36:21,195
If we turn it on in time.

985
01:36:27,907 --> 01:36:29,787
Come on. Come on!

986
01:36:47,051 --> 01:36:48,055
Hold on.

987
01:37:19,375 --> 01:37:20,434
Now!

988
01:37:50,865 --> 01:37:52,394
Son of a bitch.

989
01:37:59,790 --> 01:38:00,638
Go!

990
01:38:04,211 --> 01:38:06,600
He's got a hologram!

991
01:38:28,235 --> 01:38:30,925
You think this is the real Quaid?
It is.

992
01:39:50,776 --> 01:39:52,823
You're coming with me!

993
01:40:06,375 --> 01:40:08,548
See you at the party, Richter.

994
01:40:46,874 --> 01:40:50,095
Don't touch that!
Get away! Get back!

995
01:40:50,211 --> 01:40:51,591
What are you afraid of?

996
01:40:51,712 --> 01:40:54,051
- Turn it on.
- Impossible!

997
01:40:54,215 --> 01:40:57,423
Once the reaction starts,
it'll spread to all the turbinium in the planet.

998
01:40:57,426 --> 01:41:02,550
Mars will go into global meltdown.
That's why the aliens never turned it on.

999
01:41:02,556 --> 01:41:04,762
Do you expect me to believe you?

1000
01:41:04,765 --> 01:41:09,351
Who gives a shit what you believe?
In 30 seconds you'll be dead.

1001
01:41:09,355 --> 01:41:12,833
Then I'll blow this place up
and be home in time for corn flakes.

1002
01:41:16,320 --> 01:41:18,159
I didn't want it to end this way.

1003
01:41:18,322 --> 01:41:20,986
I wanted Hauser back.
But no.

1004
01:41:21,575 --> 01:41:23,748
You had to be Quaid!

1005
01:41:23,869 --> 01:41:26,250
- I am Quaid.
- You're nothing!

1006
01:41:26,414 --> 01:41:29,420
You're nobody!
You're a stupid dream.

1007
01:41:29,583 --> 01:41:33,507
Well, all dreams come to an end.

1008
01:42:48,371 --> 01:42:50,668
- Melina, hold on!
- No.

1009
01:42:50,790 --> 01:42:52,436
Don't do it!

1010
01:42:52,500 --> 01:42:54,680
We'll all die!

1011
01:42:55,336 --> 01:42:57,717
Everybody will die!

1012
01:44:00,860 --> 01:44:02,623
Quaid!

1013
01:45:20,424 --> 01:45:21,624
Hold on!

1014
01:49:17,510 --> 01:49:19,849
I can't believe it.
It's like a dream.

1015
01:49:21,180 --> 01:49:22,768
What's wrong?

1016
01:49:22,932 --> 01:49:26,827
I just had a terrible thought.
What if this is a dream?

1017
01:49:28,270 --> 01:49:31,457
Well, then kiss me quick
before you wake up.

